metadata.name: The Dawg In ME
metadata.description:
"The Dawg in ME" is artwork influenced by the new age saying "He/She got that DAWG in them" 
This collection is not for everyone because not everyone has that dawg in them. For the savages and the ruthless this is a fun artwork to show that you do indeed HAVE THAT DAWG IN YOU! 

Works great as a banner on socials or just a cool piece in your collection. This token does NOT have any utility attached but who really cares about that?
